Dear Customer,
We would like to inform you about a planned System Maintenance action for T=
iDB Cloud on June 11, 2026. This maintenance is crucial to enhance the stab=
ility and reliability of our services.

--------------------
*Maintenance window*
--------------------

* Start time: 2026-06-11 17:00 (UTC+8)
* End time: 2026-06-11 17:30 (UTC+8)
* Duration: 30 mins

--------------
*Impact scope*
--------------

* All TiDB Starter/Essential instances

----------------
*Impact Details*
----------------

This maintenance affects management operations on the TiDB Cloud Console an=
d OpenAPI ( *temporarily unavailable for 3-5 mins* ). TiDB Cloud connectivi=
ty and standard read/write operations will remain unaffected. You can conti=
nue to access data and run applications as usual. The primary components af=
fected are:

* Data Migration & Changefeed: Data Migration (DM), Changefeed management.
* Data Utilities: Export, Import, and Backup Schedule Setting management.
* Branch management
* Database Audit Log management

We apologize for any inconvenience this may cause. Please feel free to cont=
act us if you have any concerns.

*Best regards,*
*TiDB Cloud*

This message was sent from PingCAP, Ltd.
